name: Benevolence (NatCatCute)
description:
Explore an open world to discover your identity and obtain great divine powers. Maneuver through ancient ruins, interact with the world’s inhabitants, and heal the mistakes of your dark past. Use your Earth-given strength to purge the Corruption from the world’s creatures and the great Deities that keep your world at peace.
